sequenceDiagram
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C1 as 消费者实例A
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant C2 as 消费者实例B

    M->>C1: message_id=M1
    C1->>P: Inbox+库存+订单+Outbox
    P-->>C1: COMMIT成功
    C1--xM: ACK前宕机

    M->>C2: 重投M1
    C2->>P: INSERT Inbox(M1) ON CONFLICT
    P-->>C2: 已存在，读取原结果
    C2-->>M: ACK
